data.description: Sunshine, golf views and blue skies await as you settle into your south Florida lifestyle. Highly desirable Bay Hill model, offering 3 bedrooms plus a den, 2. 5 baths, split floorplan complimented by vaulted ceilings and tons of light. This well-priced single-family home is situated on the golf course with an expansive back yard, offering a country club lifestyle without the fees.  Unlock the full potential of this home with your unique designer touches, as it awaits a transformation to match your style and preferences. Low HOA fee includes cable, internet, manned 24-hour gate and much more. This home features a new water heater (6 months old), a 5-year-old air conditioning system, and a convenient electric car plugin.
